geometry pa\u02bbakik\u012b: ʻO ke aʻo ʻana i nā hale geometric a me nā hana i puka mai, a i wehewehe ʻia e nā helu paʻakikī
helu pa\u02bbakik\u012b: Nā helu o ke ʻano a + bi inā he helu maoli ka a a me b
\u02bb\u0101pana maoli: ʻO ka huaʻōlelo i loko o kahi helu paʻakikī ʻaʻole i loaʻa ka ʻāpana noʻonoʻo ma ke ʻano he kumu
\u02bb\u0101pana no\u02bbono\u02bbo: ʻO ka ʻāpana o ka helu paʻakikī i loaʻa ka ʻāpana noʻonoʻo ma ke ʻano he kumu
\u02bbano pa\u02bbakik\u012b: ʻO nā hakahaka i loko o ka geometry paʻakikī, he hōʻuluʻulu ʻia o nā pihi a me nā ʻili
n\u0101 \u02bbano algebraic pa\u02bbakik: ʻO nā hakahaka i loko o ka geometric paʻakikī he mau hoʻonā i nā hoohalike polynomial
hana holomorphic: Nā hana i loko o ka geometric paʻakikī i paʻakikī-ʻokoʻa
papahana ho\u02bboh\u0101like li\u02bbil: He papahana i loko o ka geometry paʻakikī no ka hoʻokaʻawale ʻana i nā ʻano like ʻole a me nā ʻano algebraic paʻakikī
moduli spaces: Nā hakahaka i loko o ka geometric paʻakikī e hoʻohālikelike i kekahi ʻano mea geometric
mana\u02bbo kalabi: ʻO kahi manaʻo i loko o ka geometry paʻakikī i hōʻoia ʻia e Shing-Tung Yau e pili ana i ke ʻano o kahi ʻano metric kūikawā ma kahi manifold paʻakikī.
hitchin-kobayashi palapala: He palapala i loko o ka geometry paʻakikī ma waena o nā pūʻolo vector holomorphic paʻa a me nā hoʻonā i kekahi hoʻohālikelike ʻokoʻa.
palapala hodge nonabelian: He palapala i loko o ka geometry paʻakikī ma waena o kekahi mau ʻano o nā ʻano like ʻole a me kekahi ʻano o nā hale algebraic
kahler-einstein metrics: ʻO nā ʻano anana kūikawā ma kahi manifold paʻakikī e hoʻokō i kekahi kūlana
